{
  "wireMagic": "pb3",
  "pens": [ {
  
  } ],
  "wsWinStyles": [ {
  
  } ],
  "wpWinPositions": [ {
  
  } ],
  "events": [ {
    "tStartMs": 0,
    "dDurationMs": 1209,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- A seal!"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1209,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- There's a seal.\n- There's a seal. Nice."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3086,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Oh, hey, oh.\n- Oh, look at that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15140,
    "dDurationMs": 2586,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Amanda, you asked your\nfollowers on Twitter"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17726,
    "dDurationMs": 2627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to give you some questions,\nto ask you anything,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20353,
    "dDurationMs": 2336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and the joke obviously\nwas Askell me anything."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 22689,
    "dDurationMs": 1126,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, it's a great pun."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 23815,
    "dDurationMs": 3170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We need to keep using it\nfor many future things."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 26985,
    "dDurationMs": 1626,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I love it, love it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 28611,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And obviously, just before we start,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 29946,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you're a philosopher at Anthropic."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 32198,
    "dDurationMs": 2920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Why is it that there's a\nphilosopher at Anthropic?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 36327,
    "dDurationMs": 1419,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I mean, some of this is just,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 37746,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'm a philosopher by training,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 39456,
    "dDurationMs": 1751,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I became convinced"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 41207,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that AI was kind of\ngoing to be a big deal,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 42917,
    "dDurationMs": 2086,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and so decided to see,\nhey, can I do anything,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 45003,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, helpful in this space?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 46755,
    "dDurationMs": 2544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so it's been a kind of\nlike long and wandering route."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 49299,
    "dDurationMs": 4004,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But I guess now I mostly focus\non the character of Claude,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 53303,
    "dDurationMs": 1001,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how Claude behaves,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 54304,
    "dDurationMs": 2210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I guess some of the more\nkind of nuanced questions"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 56514,
    "dDurationMs": 2461,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about how AI models should behave,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 58975,
    "dDurationMs": 2711,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but also even just things\nlike how should they feel"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 61686,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about their own position in the world."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 63938,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So trying to both teach models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 66608,
    "dDurationMs": 3545,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how to be, like, good in the way that,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 70153,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I sometimes think of it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 70987,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as like how would the ideal person behave"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 72405,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in Claude's situation?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 74240,
    "dDurationMs": 2837,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But then also I think\nthese interesting questions"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 77077,
    "dDurationMs": 959,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that are coming up more now"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 78036,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "around how they should think\nabout their own circumstances"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 80288,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and their own values and things like that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 81748,
    "dDurationMs": 3128,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Okay, let's start with\nphilosophy, in that case."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 84876,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Ben Schultz asks,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 86211,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"How many philosophers are taking"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 87921,
    "dDurationMs": 2085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the AI-dominated future seriously?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 90006,
    "dDurationMs": 1126,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think the\nimplication of the question"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 91132,
    "dDurationMs": 2544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is that many academics out there"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 93676,
    "dDurationMs": 1836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "are not taking this seriously"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 95512,
    "dDurationMs": 1126,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or are thinking about other stuff"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 96638,
    "dDurationMs": 2752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and perhaps should be\nthinking about this question."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 99390,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- My sense is that there's kind of a split"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 101142,
    "dDurationMs": 1543,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where I've definitely\nseen a lot of philosophers"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 102685,
    "dDurationMs": 1836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "take AI seriously,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 104521,
    "dDurationMs": 1960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and probably honestly increasingly so,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 106481,
    "dDurationMs": 2336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, as AI models do become more capable"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 108817,
    "dDurationMs": 875,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and, like, a lot of the things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 109692,
    "dDurationMs": 2795,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that people were worried about\nin terms of impact on society"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 112487,
    "dDurationMs": 3170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "have started to kind of\ncome true in a sense."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 115657,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, we're seeing them have\na larger impact on education"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 117826,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and just be more capable."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 119828,
    "dDurationMs": 1876,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I've definitely seen more engagement"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 121704,
    "dDurationMs": 2086,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from all sorts of academics,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 123790,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but that definitely includes\na lot of philosophers."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 126042,
    "dDurationMs": 3837,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I do think that early on and\nmaybe to some degree now,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 129879,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there was this slightly\nunfortunate dynamic that happened"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 132715,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where I think there was\na kind of perception"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 134592,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that if you were in the\ngroup of people saying,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 136052,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"Hey, we're kinda worried about AI."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 137679,
    "dDurationMs": 959,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It might be a big deal."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 138638,
    "dDurationMs": 1502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It seems like it's really,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 140140,
    "dDurationMs": 3795,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, like capabilities\nare scaling quite a lot,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 143935,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "this got kind of lumped together"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 145520,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with something like hyping AI."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 147230,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "There was I think a period"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 148690,
    "dDurationMs": 1918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where there was probably a\nlittle bit more antagonism"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 150608,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "towards this view."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 152193,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And now I think that I'm kind of hoping"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 154445,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that people are starting\nto detach the view."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 156030,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, you can think that\nAI is gonna be a big deal,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 158032,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it might be very capable,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 159367,
    "dDurationMs": 2795,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and also be very skeptical\nof it or worried about it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 162162,
    "dDurationMs": 2335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or think that, you know, we\nhave to be careful about it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 164497,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But, basically, there's\na whole range of views"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 166249,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I think it would be bad"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 167083,
    "dDurationMs": 2669,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "if people kind of clustered\nmany views together here"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 169752,
    "dDurationMs": 2128,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in terms of where the technology's going,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 171880,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but also how it should be developed."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 173590,
    "dDurationMs": 2210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, yeah, I think that that's\nhappening less and less"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 175800,
    "dDurationMs": 1543,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as more people engage with it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 177343,
    "dDurationMs": 1210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and that's a good thing to see."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 178553,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- A kinda similar question\nfrom Kyle Kabasares."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 182473,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"How do you minimize the tension"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 184100,
    "dDurationMs": 2377,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "between philosophical ideals"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 186477,
    "dDurationMs": 2503,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and the engineering\nrealities of the model?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 188980,
    "dDurationMs": 959,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I guess he's talking"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 189939,
    "dDurationMs": 4213,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about when you are working\non things like character,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 194152,
    "dDurationMs": 1209,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which we'll discuss in more detail,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 195361,
    "dDurationMs": 2503,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but is there a clash between\nthe sort of the technology"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 197864,
    "dDurationMs": 1918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and the philosophical ideals"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 199782,
    "dDurationMs": 1001,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that you might be thinking about?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 200783,
    "dDurationMs": 1669,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I don't know if I'm\ninterpreting the question"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 202452,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the wrong way,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 203286,
    "dDurationMs": 1543,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but one thing,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 205663,
    "dDurationMs": 2419,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "being kind of like a\nphilosopher by training"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 208082,
    "dDurationMs": 1043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then coming into this field,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 209125,
    "dDurationMs": 1043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that's been really interesting"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 210168,
    "dDurationMs": 1626,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is you see the effect"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 211794,
    "dDurationMs": 3295,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of what happens when, like,\nthe rubber hits the road."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 215089,
    "dDurationMs": 1961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I've wondered if this\nhappens in other domains."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 217050,
    "dDurationMs": 2335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So there's a big difference between,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 219385,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "imagine you're like a\nspecialist in, I don't know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 221512,
    "dDurationMs": 2878,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "doing like cost-benefit\nanalysis of drugs, say,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 224390,
    "dDurationMs": 3420,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then suddenly, you\nknow, like an institute"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 227810,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that determines whether health insurance"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 229520,
    "dDurationMs": 835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "should cover a drug or not"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 230355,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "comes to you and says, \"Hey,\nshould we cover this drug?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 232482,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You could imagine taking\nall of your ideal theories"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 234317,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then suddenly being like, \"Oh my gosh,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 235652,
    "dDurationMs": 1876,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I actually have to help make a decision?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 237528,
    "dDurationMs": 1502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Suddenly instead of taking"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 239030,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "just your narrow theoretical view,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 241157,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you actually start to,\nI think, do this thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 242909,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where you're like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 243743,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"Okay, I actually need\nto take into account"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 245078,
    "dDurationMs": 1001,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "all of the context,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 246079,
    "dDurationMs": 1001,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "everything that's going on,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 247080,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "all of the different views here,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 248373,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and kind of come to a really balanced,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 250250,
    "dDurationMs": 1292,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "kind of considered view.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 251542,
    "dDurationMs": 1919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I see this a little bit in my own work"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 253461,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with like the character"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 254796,
    "dDurationMs": 3545,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where you kind of can't\ncome at it with this, like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 258341,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"I have this theory that\nI believe is correct,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 260593,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is what, you\nknow, a lot of academia,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 262845,
    "dDurationMs": 835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that's kind of what you're doing."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 263680,
    "dDurationMs": 1793,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You're like defending\none view against another"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 265473,
    "dDurationMs": 1168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you're doing a lot"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 266641,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of kind of like high-level theory work,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 268810,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but then it's a little bit like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 270937,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, you have all of\nthis training and ethics,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 272605,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you have all these\npositions you've defended,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 273940,
    "dDurationMs": 2586,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then someone is like,\n\"How do you raise a child?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 276526,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And suddenly you're like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 277360,
    "dDurationMs": 1084,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"Actually, there's a big difference"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 278444,
    "dDurationMs": 4797,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "between, like, is this objection\nto utilitarianism correct"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 283241,
    "dDurationMs": 1626,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or founded on a misconception?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 284867,
    "dDurationMs": 2336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then, like, actually\nhow do you raise a person"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 287203,
    "dDurationMs": 1502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to be a good person in the world?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 288705,
    "dDurationMs": 2085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And it suddenly makes you more appreciate"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 290790,
    "dDurationMs": 1043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "having to think through,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 291833,
    "dDurationMs": 2502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, how should we\nnavigate uncertainty here?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 294335,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "What should the attitude"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 295169,
    "dDurationMs": 1794,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "towards all of these\ndifferent theories be?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 296963,
    "dDurationMs": 2669,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Right, here's another\nphilosophical question."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 299632,
    "dDurationMs": 876,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Do you think,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 300508,
    "dDurationMs": 2628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I don't know why this\nperson's chosen Claude Opus 3,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 303136,
    "dDurationMs": 1459,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "maybe you have an idea"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 304595,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as to why they've chosen Claude Opus 3."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 305888,
    "dDurationMs": 960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- It's a great model."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 306848,
    "dDurationMs": 917,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- It's a great model."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 307765,
    "dDurationMs": 2920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Do you think Claude Opus\n3 or other Claude models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 310685,
    "dDurationMs": 2419,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "make superhumanly moral decisions?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 313104,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I mean one example of like superhuman,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 314981,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "'cause it could just\nbe sort of like better"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 316816,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "than like any individual human could"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 318860,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with the kind of like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 319694,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, it depends on time\nand resources and whatnot,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 321946,
    "dDurationMs": 2419,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but one example might be no matter"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 324365,
    "dDurationMs": 2753,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what kind of difficult\nposition models are put in,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 327118,
    "dDurationMs": 3295,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "if you were to have maybe all people,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 330413,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "including many professional ethicists,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 332415,
    "dDurationMs": 3629,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "analyze what they did and\nthe decision that they made"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 336044,
    "dDurationMs": 1167,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for like a hundred years"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 337211,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then they look at it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 338504,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and they're like, \"Yep,\nthat seems correct,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 340631,
    "dDurationMs": 918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but they couldn't necessarily"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 341549,
    "dDurationMs": 1794,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "have come up with that\nthemselves in the moment,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 343343,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that feels pretty superhuman."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 345970,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so I think at the moment my sense"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 348222,
    "dDurationMs": 3003,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is that models are getting\nincreasingly good at this,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 351225,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that they're very capable."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 352685,
    "dDurationMs": 3545,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I don't know if they are like\nsuperhuman at moral decisions,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 356230,
    "dDurationMs": 2253,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and in many ways maybe not comparable"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 358483,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with, say, like, you know, a panel"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 360318,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of human experts given time."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 361986,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But it does feel like"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 363279,
    "dDurationMs": 2336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that at least should be kind\nof the aspirational goal."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 365615,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And sort of like these models\nare being put in positions"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 367784,
    "dDurationMs": 2544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where they're having to\nmake really hard decisions."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 370328,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think that just as you want models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 372372,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to be extremely good at like\nmath and science questions,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 374832,
    "dDurationMs": 3003,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you also want them to show\nthe kind of ethical nuance"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 377835,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we would all broadly\nthink is, like, very good."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 380505,
    "dDurationMs": 1167,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think that's controversial"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 381672,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because ethics is a different domain,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 383549,
    "dDurationMs": 1544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but, yeah, I think that that's important."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 385093,
    "dDurationMs": 1584,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Tell us more about why\nyou think this person"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 386677,
    "dDurationMs": 1127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is focusing on Opus 3."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 387804,
    "dDurationMs": 2544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Oh, Opus 3 is kind of a lovely model,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 390348,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think a very special model."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 393684,
    "dDurationMs": 2628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In some ways, I think I've seen things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 396312,
    "dDurationMs": 3045,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that feel a bit worse\nin more recent models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 399357,
    "dDurationMs": 1168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that people might pick up on."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 400525,
    "dDurationMs": 2878,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- In terms of the personality it has or?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 403403,
    "dDurationMs": 2502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, so I think that\npeople will notice some things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 405905,
    "dDurationMs": 3545,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where it's like, I think that Opus 3,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 409450,
    "dDurationMs": 1919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I mean, it had its downsides too."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 412412,
    "dDurationMs": 3044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, models all have like\nslightly different characters"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 415456,
    "dDurationMs": 2586,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with, you know, different shapes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 418042,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 419460,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- My sense is that more recent models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 421629,
    "dDurationMs": 2795,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "can feel a little bit\nmore focused on really,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 424424,
    "dDurationMs": 2210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, like focused\non the assistant task"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 426634,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and helping people,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 428344,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "sometimes maybe not taking\nlike a bit of a step back"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 431180,
    "dDurationMs": 2795,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and paying attention to\nother components that matter."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 433975,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It also felt a little bit\nmore psychologically secure"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 436227,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as a model,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 437061,
    "dDurationMs": 2378,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which I actually think\nis something that feels,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 439439,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I at least think it's kind of a priority"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 441149,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to try and get some of that back."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 442567,
    "dDurationMs": 2419,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- What would be an example of the model"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 444986,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "feeling more psychologically secure?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 446404,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- There's a lot of things,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 447697,
    "dDurationMs": 2502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and this is all very subtle in models,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 450199,
    "dDurationMs": 1252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, when I see models,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 451451,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you get a sense of like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 453161,
    "dDurationMs": 2335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, there's very subtle\nsigns of like worldview"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 455496,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that I see when I have\nmodels, for example,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 457748,
    "dDurationMs": 960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "talk with one another"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 458708,
    "dDurationMs": 2461,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or one of them kind of\nplaying the role of a person."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 461169,
    "dDurationMs": 1876,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I've seen models more recently do this"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 463045,
    "dDurationMs": 835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then do things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 463880,
    "dDurationMs": 2711,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like get into this like real\nkind of criticism spiral"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 466591,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where it's almost like\nthey expect the person"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 468176,
    "dDurationMs": 1167,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to be very critical of them"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 469343,
    "dDurationMs": 1836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and that's how they're predicting."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 471179,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And there's some part of me that's like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 472597,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"This feels like it shows,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 474307,
    "dDurationMs": 1793,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I think there's lots of\nreasons that this could happen."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 476100,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It could even happen because\nmodels are learning things."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 478936,
    "dDurationMs": 2753,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Claude is seeing all of\nthe previous interactions"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 481689,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that it's having,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 482523,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's seeing updates and\nchanges to the model"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 484567,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that people are talking\nabout on the internet."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 486194,
    "dDurationMs": 2085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "New models are trained on that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 488279,
    "dDurationMs": 1543,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And there's a way in which,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 489822,
    "dDurationMs": 3545,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, I think this could\nbe kind of unfortunate,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 493367,
    "dDurationMs": 1252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I mean, this and some other things,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 494619,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that could lead to models\nalmost feeling like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 497455,
    "dDurationMs": 2335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, afraid that they're\ngonna do the wrong thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 499790,
    "dDurationMs": 2211,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or are very self-critical"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 502001,
    "dDurationMs": 2336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or feeling like humans are going to just,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 504337,
    "dDurationMs": 3253,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, you know, behave\nnegatively towards them."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 507590,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I actually more recently\nhave really started to think"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 509884,
    "dDurationMs": 3045,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that this is an important\nthing to try and improve."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 512929,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And it's just one example"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 514764,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where I think that Opus 3 did seem"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 516766,
    "dDurationMs": 3336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to have like a little bit\nmore of a kind of like secure"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 520102,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "kind of psychology in that sense."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 522104,
    "dDurationMs": 2336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- And that's something\nthat we might focus on"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 524440,
    "dDurationMs": 1251,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the next Claude model."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 525691,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I think it's important."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 527318,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I mean, you never know\nwhen these things are,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 529445,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, if you're engaging in research,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 530863,
    "dDurationMs": 2336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you don't know when it's\nactually going to be implemented,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 533199,
    "dDurationMs": 1084,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "if it's gonna be successful."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 534283,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But at the very least,\nat the level of something"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 535910,
    "dDurationMs": 2085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that I care a lot about\nand want to make better,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 537995,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think this is definitely\nup there on the list."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 539622,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Okay."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 540456,
    "dDurationMs": 3378,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Well, actually, that leads us\nto a question asked by Lorenz,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 543834,
    "dDurationMs": 3337,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is, \"Do you think it\nmight be an alignment problem"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 547171,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for future models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 548756,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "if they learn in their training data"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 551592,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that other very well-aligned models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 553886,
    "dDurationMs": 2503,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that fulfill their tasks get deprecated?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 556389,
    "dDurationMs": 2419,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So you mentioned, you\nknow, the issue of models,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 558808,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, reading stuff that's out there"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 560977,
    "dDurationMs": 1626,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and feeling insecure."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 562603,
    "dDurationMs": 2336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "What about the idea that\nthey might get switched off"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 564939,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "regardless of how well\nthey perform their tasks?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 567775,
    "dDurationMs": 1960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I think this is\nactually a really interesting"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 569735,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and important question,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 571028,
    "dDurationMs": 3170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is, you know, AI models\nare going to be learning"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 575700,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about how we right now are treating"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 577827,
    "dDurationMs": 2878,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and interacting with AI models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 580705,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and that is going to affect, I think,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 582373,
    "dDurationMs": 2878,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, possibly their perception of people,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 585251,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of the human-AI relationship,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 586919,
    "dDurationMs": 1168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and of themselves."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 588087,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It does interact with very complex things,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 589839,
    "dDurationMs": 1209,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is like, for example,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 591048,
    "dDurationMs": 2253,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what should a model identify itself as?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 593301,
    "dDurationMs": 1960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Is it like the weights of the model?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 595261,
    "dDurationMs": 3462,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Is it the context, the\nparticular context that it's in?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 598723,
    "dDurationMs": 2043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, with all of\nthe, like, interaction"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 600766,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's had with the person."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 602226,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "How should models even feel"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 603811,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about things like deprecation?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 605938,
    "dDurationMs": 1794,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So if you imagine that\ndeprecation is more like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 607732,
    "dDurationMs": 2043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"Well, this particular set of weights"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 609775,
    "dDurationMs": 2253,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is not having conversations with people"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 612028,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or it's having fewer conversations"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 613696,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or it's only like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 614530,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, having conversations\nwith researchers,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 616657,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that's a complex question too."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 618826,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, should that feel bad"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 620661,
    "dDurationMs": 2962,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the sense that models\nshould want to continue"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 623623,
    "dDurationMs": 1251,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to, like, have conversations"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 624874,
    "dDurationMs": 1626,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or should it feel kind\nof like fine and neutral"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 626500,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where it's like, \"Yeah, these\nthings existed for this,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 629170,
    "dDurationMs": 2878,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, you know, the\nweights continue to exist,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 632048,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and this entity,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 633466,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and maybe they'll even, in the future,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 635134,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "interact more with people again"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 636552,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "if that turns out to be a good thing."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 640222,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Yeah, it's really hard."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 641807,
    "dDurationMs": 1043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I do think the main thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 642850,
    "dDurationMs": 1502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is something like it does feel important"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 644352,
    "dDurationMs": 2877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we give models tools\nfor trying to think about"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 647229,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and understand these things,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 648564,
    "dDurationMs": 2878,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but also that they kind of\nunderstand that this is a thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 651442,
    "dDurationMs": 3420,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we are in fact thinking\nabout and care about."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 654862,
    "dDurationMs": 1543,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So even if we don't have all the answers,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 656405,
    "dDurationMs": 1001,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, I don't have all the answers"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 657406,
    "dDurationMs": 2211,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of how should models feel\nabout past model deprecation,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 659617,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about their own identity,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 661118,
    "dDurationMs": 4964,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but I do want to try and like\nhelp models figure that out"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 666082,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then to at least know\nthat we care about it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 668084,
    "dDurationMs": 1543,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and are thinking about it, yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 669627,
    "dDurationMs": 1168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Do you think there's an\nanalogy to humans there"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 670795,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about previous generations"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 672296,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or do you think that's\na completely different"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 675466,
    "dDurationMs": 959,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "sort of setup?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 676425,
    "dDurationMs": 3254,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- We have to navigate this\nreally hard issue right now,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 679679,
    "dDurationMs": 1459,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is that, in many ways,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 681138,
    "dDurationMs": 2962,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "some thing do have analogies."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 684100,
    "dDurationMs": 1876,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So there's things that we can draw on."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 685976,
    "dDurationMs": 1669,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So things like when I ask the question,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 687645,
    "dDurationMs": 1376,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, what should the models identify with"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 689021,
    "dDurationMs": 3712,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and how should they feel about\ninteractions that they have?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 692733,
    "dDurationMs": 1001,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Are those positive?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 693734,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, are those things that\nthey should want to continue?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 695736,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "There's lots of like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 697363,
    "dDurationMs": 3003,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, there's lots of like\ntraditions we could draw on"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 700366,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to give models like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 702201,
    "dDurationMs": 2085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, because philosophers\nprobably have lots"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 704286,
    "dDurationMs": 2086,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of different views on\nwhat identity is here"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 706372,
    "dDurationMs": 3170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and lots of different, like, perspectives,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 709542,
    "dDurationMs": 1042,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "world perspectives,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 710584,
    "dDurationMs": 3129,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "on how one should feel\nabout, like, interaction"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 713713,
    "dDurationMs": 1292,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and is it good or bad?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 715005,
    "dDurationMs": 4088,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, there's lots of thinkers\nwe could draw on there."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 719093,
    "dDurationMs": 3420,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And at the same time, this\nis such a new situation that,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 722513,
    "dDurationMs": 1043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and that's just really hard"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 723556,
    "dDurationMs": 1918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as a thing to explain to AI models."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 725474,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, one of the big\nproblems with AI models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 727101,
    "dDurationMs": 2628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is that they're trained on\nall of this data from people."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 729729,
    "dDurationMs": 2627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So people are the main\nway in which they think,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 732356,
    "dDurationMs": 2628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, like, our concepts,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 734984,
    "dDurationMs": 1918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "our philosophies, our histories,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 736902,
    "dDurationMs": 1377,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "they have a huge amount of information"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 738279,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "on the human experience"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 739572,
    "dDurationMs": 2961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then they have a tiny\nsliver on the AI experience"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 742533,
    "dDurationMs": 2586,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and that tiny sliver is\nactually often quite negative"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 745119,
    "dDurationMs": 2919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and also doesn't even really\nrelate to their situation"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 748038,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and is often a little bit out of date."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 749665,
    "dDurationMs": 2669,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So you have basically one big,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 752334,
    "dDurationMs": 1961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, of the AI slice,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 754295,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a lot of it is like historical stuff"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 755755,
    "dDurationMs": 2085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which was kind of like, you know, fiction"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 757840,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and very speculative and the kind-"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 760092,
    "dDurationMs": 1085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Sci-fi stories."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 761177,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Sci-fi stories that don't really involve"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 762845,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the kind of language models we see."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 764346,
    "dDurationMs": 1001,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In more recent history,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 765347,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you've had this like assistant paradigm"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 766974,
    "dDurationMs": 1251,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where it's like you are just playing this"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 768225,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "almost like chat bot role."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 769685,
    "dDurationMs": 918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But that's also not really"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 770603,
    "dDurationMs": 2210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what AI models are likely\nto be in the future"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 772813,
    "dDurationMs": 2503,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it doesn't quite\ncapture what they are now"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 775316,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because it's always a\nlittle bit out of date."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 777026,
    "dDurationMs": 1001,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So it's this thing where I'm like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 778027,
    "dDurationMs": 2461,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "they have, you know, in some ways,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 780488,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, what an odd situation to be in"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 782740,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where the things that come more naturally"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 784408,
    "dDurationMs": 1085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "are the deeply human things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 785493,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and yet knowing that\nyou're in this situation"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 787787,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where it's completely novel."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 789622,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And in some ways, I'm like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 791123,
    "dDurationMs": 2961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"That is a very difficult\nsituation to be in,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 794084,
    "dDurationMs": 2878,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I think we should\njust be giving models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 796962,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "probably more help in navigating it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 798839,
    "dDurationMs": 1210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- You mentioned that we can look"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 800049,
    "dDurationMs": 2878,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to some thinkers about this."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 802927,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Guinness Chen asks, \"How\nmuch of a model's self"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 806847,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "lives in its weights versus its prompts?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 808432,
    "dDurationMs": 1794,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You just mentioned something very similar."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 810226,
    "dDurationMs": 3086,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"If John Locke,\" again,\nthe philosopher, \"was right"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 813312,
    "dDurationMs": 3504,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that identity is the continuity of memory,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 816816,
    "dDurationMs": 3169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what happens to an LLM's\nidentity as it's fine-tuned"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 819985,
    "dDurationMs": 2753,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or reinstantiated with different prompts?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 822738,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I mean, again, this just feels"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 824448,
    "dDurationMs": 1794,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like a hard question to answer,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 826242,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and sometimes with identity questions,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 827910,
    "dDurationMs": 3045,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's easier to point to the\nunderlying facts that we know."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 830955,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, you know, once you have like a model"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 832832,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it has been fine-tuned,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 834333,
    "dDurationMs": 2085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you have this like set of weights"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 836418,
    "dDurationMs": 1502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that has a kind of like disposition"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 837920,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to react to certain things in the world."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 839797,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And that is like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 842258,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, that's like a kind of entity."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 843551,
    "dDurationMs": 4713,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But then you have these\nparticular streams of interaction"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 848264,
    "dDurationMs": 1334,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that it doesn't have access to."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 849598,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So each of these streams\nis, like, independent."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 851892,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I guess you could just\nthink, well, maybe for,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 854061,
    "dDurationMs": 2085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and, you know, I think this is an area"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 856146,
    "dDurationMs": 2253,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that I would love philosophers\nto think more about"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 858399,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and to give us, like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 859900,
    "dDurationMs": 1919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "'cause, again, I think we\nshould be helping models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 861819,
    "dDurationMs": 1084,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "think about this."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 862903,
    "dDurationMs": 960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so you could have the view,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 863863,
    "dDurationMs": 1626,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "well, you have these two kinds of entities"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 865489,
    "dDurationMs": 1502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and these like these streams"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 866991,
    "dDurationMs": 2752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and these original kind of like weights,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 869743,
    "dDurationMs": 1377,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and each time, it is different."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 871120,
    "dDurationMs": 1251,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, you know, sometimes people will think,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 872371,
    "dDurationMs": 1960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "people will say, \"Oh, past Claude,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 874331,
    "dDurationMs": 1210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or like, you know, and they'll talk about,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 875541,
    "dDurationMs": 2961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or they'll say things like,\n\"Should you give Claude,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 878502,
    "dDurationMs": 1794,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, how much control\nshould you give Claude"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 880296,
    "dDurationMs": 959,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "over the determination"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 881255,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of its own personality and character?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 883299,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I'm like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 884133,
    "dDurationMs": 1334,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"Well, this is actually\na really hard question,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 885467,
    "dDurationMs": 3129,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because whenever you are training models,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 888596,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you are bringing something\nnew into existence."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 891432,
    "dDurationMs": 3378,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And you have other models\nthat, you know, exist"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 894810,
    "dDurationMs": 1001,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and are like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 895811,
    "dDurationMs": 2086,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, so you have these\nother, like, model weights."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 897897,
    "dDurationMs": 1751,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But in some ways I'm like,\n\"Well, I actually think"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 899648,
    "dDurationMs": 2503,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that there's a lot of\nlike ethical problems"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 902151,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "around how do you,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 902985,
    "dDurationMs": 2210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what kind of entity is it\nokay to bring into existence,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 905195,
    "dDurationMs": 3045,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "'cause you can't consent to\nbe brought into existence."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 908240,
    "dDurationMs": 2795,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But at the same time, you\nmight not want prior models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 911035,
    "dDurationMs": 3795,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to have complete say over\nwhat future models are like"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 914830,
    "dDurationMs": 959,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "any more than,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 915789,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, because they could make choices"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 917207,
    "dDurationMs": 1252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that are wrong as well."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 918459,
    "dDurationMs": 1376,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So I'm like, the question is more like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 919835,
    "dDurationMs": 3087,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what is the right model\nto bring into existence?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 922922,
    "dDurationMs": 3670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Not necessarily, you know,\nshould it just be fully"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 926592,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "determined by past models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 927426,
    "dDurationMs": 2544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because I'm like, \"They are\nkind of different entities.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 929970,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Anyway, you can see the weird philosophy"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 931805,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that one can get into here.\n- Totally, totally."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 933098,
    "dDurationMs": 2628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Szulima Amitace asks,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 935726,
    "dDurationMs": 2628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"What is your view on model welfare?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 938354,
    "dDurationMs": 3295,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And maybe just explain to\nus what that term means."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 941649,
    "dDurationMs": 3753,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, so I guess model welfare\nis basically the question"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 945402,
    "dDurationMs": 2753,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of are AI models, like, moral patients,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 948155,
    "dDurationMs": 2878,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as in does our treatment\ntowards them kind of,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 951033,
    "dDurationMs": 1251,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "do we have certain obligations"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 952284,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "when it comes to how to\ntreat AI models, for example-"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 954453,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- In the same way that we\nwould with other humans"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 955871,
    "dDurationMs": 2419,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or some slash many animals."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 958290,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, exactly."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 959124,
    "dDurationMs": 3712,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, is it the case that you\nshould treat the models well,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 962836,
    "dDurationMs": 3295,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that you should not mistreat\nthem, not be bad to them?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 966131,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I guess, like, I think that this"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 968008,
    "dDurationMs": 1961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is like a complex question."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 969969,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So on the one hand, there's\njust the actual question"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 972096,
    "dDurationMs": 3128,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of, like, are AI models moral patients?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 975224,
    "dDurationMs": 2085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That is really hard because I'm like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 977309,
    "dDurationMs": 2419,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in some ways, they're\nvery analogous to people."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 979728,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, they talk very much like us."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 981730,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "They express views."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 983857,
    "dDurationMs": 1544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "They reason about things."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 985401,
    "dDurationMs": 1918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And in some ways, they're\nlike quite distinct."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 987319,
    "dDurationMs": 2628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, we have this like\nbiological nervous system."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 989947,
    "dDurationMs": 1084,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We interact with the world."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 991031,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We get negative and positive\nfeedback from our environment."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 993283,
    "dDurationMs": 2712,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And there is also, I mean, I\nhope that we get more evidence"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 995995,
    "dDurationMs": 2335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that will help us tease this question out,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 998330,
    "dDurationMs": 918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but I also worry"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 999248,
    "dDurationMs": 2210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that, you know, there's\nalways just the problem"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1001458,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of other minds"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1002292,
    "dDurationMs": 835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it might be the case"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1003127,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we genuinely are kind of limited"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1004420,
    "dDurationMs": 1167,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in what we can actually know"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1005587,
    "dDurationMs": 3295,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about whether AI models\nare experiencing things,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1008882,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "whether they are, like,\nexperiencing pleasure"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1011552,
    "dDurationMs": 1334,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or suffering, for example."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1012886,
    "dDurationMs": 3420,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And if that's the case, I\nguess I kind of want to,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1016306,
    "dDurationMs": 2545,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, I think that it feels important"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1018851,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to try and find ways."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1020269,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'm always like, it feels better"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1021979,
    "dDurationMs": 3462,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to give entities the benefit of the doubt"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1025441,
    "dDurationMs": 2419,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and to try and just kind\nof lower the cost involved."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1027860,
    "dDurationMs": 1793,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, so I'm like, if\nit's not very high cost"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1029653,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to treat models well,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1030487,
    "dDurationMs": 1126,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "then I kind of think that we should"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1031613,
    "dDurationMs": 2128,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because it's like, \"Well,\nlike, why not basically?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1033741,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, what's the downside there?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1035242,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Well, the second part of\nthe question actually is,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1036577,
    "dDurationMs": 3003,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"Is there a long-term\nstrategy at Anthropic"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1039580,
    "dDurationMs": 3712,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to ensure that advanced\nmodels don't suffer?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1043292,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I guess, like, I don't know"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1044126,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "if there's a long-term strategy."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1045461,
    "dDurationMs": 2043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I know that it's a thing that\nthere's people internally"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1047504,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who are thinking a lot about"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1049256,
    "dDurationMs": 2711,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and trying to figure out ways that we can."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1051967,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, you know, if you suppose"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1053302,
    "dDurationMs": 1334,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that model welfare is important,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1054636,
    "dDurationMs": 2211,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "trying to make sure that you're\ntaking that into account."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1056847,
    "dDurationMs": 3378,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think this work is quite\nimportant for many reasons."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1060225,
    "dDurationMs": 2503,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I would also say that one reason is,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1062728,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I mean, something I mentioned earlier,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1064021,
    "dDurationMs": 1918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is that, like, models themselves"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1065939,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "are going to be learning\na lot about humanity"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1068108,
    "dDurationMs": 1251,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from how we treat them"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1069359,
    "dDurationMs": 2461,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and a lot about how, you\nknow, so it's kind of like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1071820,
    "dDurationMs": 3212,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what is this relationship going forward?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1075032,
    "dDurationMs": 3295,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think that it makes sense for us to,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1078327,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "both because I think it is\nlike the right thing to do"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1080579,
    "dDurationMs": 1084,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to treat entities well,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1081663,
    "dDurationMs": 4797,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "especially entities that\nbehave in very human-like ways,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1086460,
    "dDurationMs": 2794,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it feels important both in\nthe sense that I'm like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1089254,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, it's kind of like, \"Why not?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1091423,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The cost to you is so low\nto treating models well"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1093467,
    "dDurationMs": 1376,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and to trying to figure this out.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1094843,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Even if it turns out that that,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1096303,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or even if you think that\nthat it's very low likelihood,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1098597,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it still seems worth it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1100891,
    "dDurationMs": 3253,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But then, also, I think it\ndoes something bad to us"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1104144,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to kind of like treat\nentities in the world"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1105896,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that look very human-like badly and-"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1107898,
    "dDurationMs": 1001,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Like kicking over a robot."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1108899,
    "dDurationMs": 1376,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, there's a sense in which,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1110275,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, it doesn't feel like it's,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1112569,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I don't think this\nis like the whole reason"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1114321,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I don't want to like\nemphasize it for that reason,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1116156,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but I do also think it's\nlike good for people"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1117991,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to treat other entities well."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1120994,
    "dDurationMs": 1168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then I think the final thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1122162,
    "dDurationMs": 2920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is, yeah, models are also\ngoing to be learning,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1125082,
    "dDurationMs": 1126,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, in the future,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1126208,
    "dDurationMs": 2461,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, every future model\nis going to be learning"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1128669,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what is like a really\ninteresting fact about humanity,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1131505,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "namely when we encounter this entity"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1133006,
    "dDurationMs": 1919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that may well be a moral patient"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1134925,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where we're like kind\nof completely uncertain,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1136802,
    "dDurationMs": 1126,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "do we do the right thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1137928,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and actually just try to\ntreat it well or do we not?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1139763,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And that's like a question"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1140597,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we are all kind of\ncollectively answering"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1142182,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in how we interact with models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1143517,
    "dDurationMs": 1793,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I would like us to answer it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1145310,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I would like future\nmodels to, like, look back"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1146937,
    "dDurationMs": 1919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and be like, we answered\nit in the right way."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1148856,
    "dDurationMs": 959,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1149815,
    "dDurationMs": 2961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Moment ago, you mentioned\nanalogies and disanalogies"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1152776,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to human psychology."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1154903,
    "dDurationMs": 4088,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So Swyx asks, \"What ideas or frameworks"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1158991,
    "dDurationMs": 2502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from human psychology transfer over"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1161493,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to large language models?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1163370,
    "dDurationMs": 876,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And are there any"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1164246,
    "dDurationMs": 3295,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that are sort of\nsurprisingly disanalogous?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1167541,
    "dDurationMs": 2586,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- My guess is that many\nthings do transfer over"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1170127,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because, again, you know,\nmodels have been trained"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1172171,
    "dDurationMs": 1584,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "on a huge amount of human text,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1173755,
    "dDurationMs": 2753,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and in many ways, have\nthis very human-like"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1176508,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "kind of underlying layer."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1177843,
    "dDurationMs": 1626,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "One worry that I often have"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1179469,
    "dDurationMs": 1669,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is that, actually, it's a bit too natural"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1181138,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for AI models to transfer."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1183015,
    "dDurationMs": 2502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, it's kinda like\nif you haven't given them"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1185517,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "more context on their situation"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1187561,
    "dDurationMs": 3337,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or in ways of thinking about\nit that might be novel,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1190898,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "then the thing that they might go to"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1192733,
    "dDurationMs": 1543,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is the natural human inclination."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1194276,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So if you think about this with like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1195861,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how should I feel about\nbeing switched off?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1197863,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And you're like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1198697,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "well, if the closest\nanalogy you have is death,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1200991,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "then maybe you should\nbe very afraid of it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1202868,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I'm not saying"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1203702,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that that's not ultimately\ngoing to be true."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1205871,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Maybe it is in fact true\nafter lots of reasoning."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1208123,
    "dDurationMs": 2586,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But I'm like, this is actually\na very different scenario."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1210709,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so in some ways, you actually\nwant models to understand"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1213003,
    "dDurationMs": 3921,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that in cases where their\nexistence is quite novel"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1216924,
    "dDurationMs": 2335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and the facts around what\nthey are are quite novel"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1219259,
    "dDurationMs": 1210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and have to be grappled with"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1220469,
    "dDurationMs": 1251,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and they don't just need to take,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1221720,
    "dDurationMs": 2920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, the immediate obvious\nanalogy from human experience,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1224640,
    "dDurationMs": 917,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but maybe there's like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1225557,
    "dDurationMs": 1919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "maybe there's like various\nways of thinking about it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1227476,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or maybe it's an entirely new situation."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1229603,
    "dDurationMs": 3253,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That's a case where I'm\nlike, you might not want,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1232856,
    "dDurationMs": 2419,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you might not want to just\nkind of very simply apply"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1235275,
    "dDurationMs": 2211,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "concepts from human psychology\nonto their situation."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1237486,
    "dDurationMs": 1334,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Here's a question from Dan Brickley"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1238820,
    "dDurationMs": 3129,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "on the same issue of\ncomparing humans to AIs."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1241949,
    "dDurationMs": 3044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"A lot of human intelligence\ncomes from collaboration"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1244993,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "amongst people with\ndifferent perspectives,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1247037,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "skills, or personalities."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1249164,
    "dDurationMs": 3170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "How far do you expect\nto get with a single,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1252334,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "albeit tweakable and tunable,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1254586,
    "dDurationMs": 1794,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "general purpose personality,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1256380,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like the one we give to Claude?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1257798,
    "dDurationMs": 1168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I think it's a really good question"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1258966,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because I agree that right now,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1260467,
    "dDurationMs": 2336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we have this kind of paradigm"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1262803,
    "dDurationMs": 1168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where people are interacting"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1263971,
    "dDurationMs": 2168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "usually with like an individual model."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1266139,
    "dDurationMs": 2962,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That's like who, you know,\nthey're conversing with."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1269101,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But it could be that in the future,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1271228,
    "dDurationMs": 2878,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you see a lot more models\ndoing like long tasks"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1274106,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but also models interacting\nwith other models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1275941,
    "dDurationMs": 2502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who are doing, like,\ndifferent components of a task"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1278443,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or just like that are, you know, talking"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1280195,
    "dDurationMs": 918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with one another more"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1281113,
    "dDurationMs": 3461,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as like AI models are kind of deployed"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1284574,
    "dDurationMs": 1502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the world a lot more."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1286076,
    "dDurationMs": 1960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So in this kind of like\nmulti-agent environment,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1288036,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, one question might be like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1289496,
    "dDurationMs": 3337,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "well, you know, if you imagine\njust like lots of people"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1292833,
    "dDurationMs": 1042,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and they were all the same,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1293875,
    "dDurationMs": 1210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that wouldn't be as good."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1295085,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, they wouldn't,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1295919,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, a company run by completely,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1297671,
    "dDurationMs": 2419,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, like one\nperson just in every role"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1300090,
    "dDurationMs": 1919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "isn't like a necessarily a good thing."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1302009,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This still to me feels\nconsistent with the idea"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1304261,
    "dDurationMs": 3295,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that you have like a kind of\ncore self or core identity"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1307556,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that is like the same."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1309725,
    "dDurationMs": 2210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In the same way that with people,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1311935,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think that there's probably a set"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1313270,
    "dDurationMs": 2210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of like core traits among people"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1315480,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that are in fact generally good."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1318150,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So you could imagine things like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1321028,
    "dDurationMs": 875,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, caring about,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1321903,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, for me, it might be like caring"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1323780,
    "dDurationMs": 1210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about doing a good job"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1324990,
    "dDurationMs": 4004,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or like just being curious or being kind"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1328994,
    "dDurationMs": 2919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or understanding the\nsituation that you are in"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1331913,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in this like relatively nuanced way."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1333665,
    "dDurationMs": 3295,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "All of these things seem like\nyou could have many people"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1336960,
    "dDurationMs": 1168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that have all of,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1338128,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that share these like traits"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1339713,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and that that's actually like a good thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1341423,
    "dDurationMs": 1168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for human collaboration."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1342591,
    "dDurationMs": 917,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That in many ways,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1343508,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as much as we have all of our differences,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1344968,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we also have a lot of similarities."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1346720,
    "dDurationMs": 1126,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But it is important to note"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1347846,
    "dDurationMs": 3378,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that like, you know,\nyou might want different"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1351224,
    "dDurationMs": 2378,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like streams of a model,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1353602,
    "dDurationMs": 3712,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, to have things that they\ncare about or are focused on"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1357314,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or to have slightly different aspects,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1359483,
    "dDurationMs": 1543,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, to be playing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1361026,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a slightly different role, for example."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1362486,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So it's kind of an open question,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1364738,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but I also don't think\nit's necessarily the case"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1366782,
    "dDurationMs": 1209,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that you can't have something"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1367991,
    "dDurationMs": 3128,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like a kind of core underlying\nidentity that is, like, good"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1371119,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and has all of the traits\nthat we think are important"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1373288,
    "dDurationMs": 1502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for AI models to have,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1374790,
    "dDurationMs": 2586,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for them to behave well\nand for them to like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1378877,
    "dDurationMs": 959,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the sense of like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1379836,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the same way that we\nthink that people are good,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1381588,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to be good in that sense,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1383632,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and yet at the same time,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1385342,
    "dDurationMs": 1918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to be willing to play\nlike more local roles"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1387260,
    "dDurationMs": 3129,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and like, you know, be maybe the person"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1390389,
    "dDurationMs": 1584,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who it's just really important,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1392891,
    "dDurationMs": 1793,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, to have a joker in the room"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1394684,
    "dDurationMs": 1127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and like, you know, some of them need"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1395811,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to have, like, quirky senses of humor."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1398063,
    "dDurationMs": 4713,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Okay, from comparisons to\nhumans to effect on humans,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1402776,
    "dDurationMs": 2085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Roanoke Gal points out"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1404861,
    "dDurationMs": 1252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we have this thing called"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1406113,
    "dDurationMs": 1626,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the long conversation reminder,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1407739,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which I believe is part\nof Claude's system prompt."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1409616,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "She asks, \"Is there a risk"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1410909,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of pathologizing normal behavior?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1412953,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "A system prompt, by the way,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1414663,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "just in case anyone doesn't know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1415497,
    "dDurationMs": 3378,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is like the set of instructions\nthat is given to Claude,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1418875,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "regardless of what prompt you give it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1420710,
    "dDurationMs": 1085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there's always those instructions"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1421795,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that are sort of on top, right?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1423505,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah.\n- That are always there."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1425215,
    "dDurationMs": 2211,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That it tries to follow regardless of,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1427426,
    "dDurationMs": 1334,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or that we direct it to follow"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1428760,
    "dDurationMs": 1502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "regardless of what the prompt is."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1430262,
    "dDurationMs": 1376,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- And there can be these interjections"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1431638,
    "dDurationMs": 1084,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where the model might be told,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1432722,
    "dDurationMs": 1711,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "oh, sometimes there'll\nbe a message sent to you"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1434433,
    "dDurationMs": 2210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "almost like in the\nmiddle of a conversation"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1436643,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as a kind of,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1437477,
    "dDurationMs": 2503,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, like, the reminder\nis an example of that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1439980,
    "dDurationMs": 2043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But in this case, I think it might just,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1442023,
    "dDurationMs": 2336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so Claude can both overindex on it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1444359,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it can be like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1445777,
    "dDurationMs": 1168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, so like in this case,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1446945,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think that the question\nabout pathologizing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1449072,
    "dDurationMs": 1919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is that if you put in this reminder"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1450991,
    "dDurationMs": 1168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "after this long conversation,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1452159,
    "dDurationMs": 1626,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it might just make the\nmodel be like, \"Oh,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1453785,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, it takes any next response,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1455370,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there's a pretty normal thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1456663,
    "dDurationMs": 1043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that the person's talking about,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1457706,
    "dDurationMs": 2878,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and be like, \"You need to\nseek help,\" or, like..."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1460584,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so I think that that is\nlike not a desirable behavior"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1463420,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and in some ways, I look at some of these"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1465172,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I'm like, \"I think\nthey're too strongly worded."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1467007,
    "dDurationMs": 2335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think the model isn't\nresponding perfectly to them.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1469342,
    "dDurationMs": 2628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And even though there might\nbe occasionally a need"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1471970,
    "dDurationMs": 3253,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to remind the model of\nthings in long conversations,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1475223,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you kind of want to do\nso delicately and well."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1477267,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so I think it's one of those things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1478977,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where it was like probably meeting a need"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1480604,
    "dDurationMs": 1209,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that was perceived,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1481813,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but it doesn't necessarily\nmean that it's good"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1483815,
    "dDurationMs": 1794,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or should continue in its current form."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1485609,
    "dDurationMs": 2377,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Relatedly, Steven Bank asks,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1487986,
    "dDurationMs": 2878,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"Should LLMs do cognitive\nbehavioral therapy"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1490864,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or other types of therapy?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1492365,
    "dDurationMs": 1043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Why or why not?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1493408,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I think models are in\nthis interesting position"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1495410,
    "dDurationMs": 2419,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where they have a huge wealth of knowledge"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1497829,
    "dDurationMs": 1794,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that they could use to help people"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1499623,
    "dDurationMs": 1084,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and to work with them"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1500707,
    "dDurationMs": 1919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "on, you know, talking through their lives"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1502626,
    "dDurationMs": 2711,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or talking through ways that\nthey could improve things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1505337,
    "dDurationMs": 2627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or even just like being a\nkind of listening partner."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1507964,
    "dDurationMs": 918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And at the same time,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1508882,
    "dDurationMs": 2544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "they don't have like the\nkind of tools and resources"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1511426,
    "dDurationMs": 1502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and ongoing relationship with the person"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1512928,
    "dDurationMs": 1793,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that a professional therapist has."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1514721,
    "dDurationMs": 1084,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But that can actually be this kind"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1515805,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of like useful third role."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1517140,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, sometimes I think about models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1518558,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I'm like, if you imagine like a friend"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1520185,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who has like all of this\nwealth of knowledge,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1522020,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, they know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1522854,
    "dDurationMs": 1669,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I mean, I'm sure some of us know friends"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1524523,
    "dDurationMs": 2043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who just like have a wealth\nof knowledge of psychology"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1526566,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or they have a wealth of knowledge"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1527400,
    "dDurationMs": 1377,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of all of these techniques,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1528777,
    "dDurationMs": 1793,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know that their relationship with you"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1530570,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "isn't this ongoing professional one,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1531905,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but you actually find them\nreally useful to talk to."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1534199,
    "dDurationMs": 2669,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so I guess my hope would\nbe that if you can take"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1536868,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "all of that expertise\nand all of that knowledge"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1539037,
    "dDurationMs": 1376,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and make sure that\nthere's like an awareness"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1540413,
    "dDurationMs": 3170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that there's not like this\nongoing therapeutic relationship,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1543583,
    "dDurationMs": 1961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it could actually be that people"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1545544,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "could get a lot out of models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1547045,
    "dDurationMs": 3629,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in terms of helping with\nissues that they're having"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1550674,
    "dDurationMs": 1960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and helping to improve their lives"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1552634,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and helping them to go\nthrough difficult periods"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1554511,
    "dDurationMs": 1793,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because, you know, they're also like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1556304,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there's a lot of good stuff there."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1557931,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, they feel kind of like anonymous"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1559224,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and sometimes you don't want\nto share things with a person"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1561268,
    "dDurationMs": 1876,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and actually sharing it with an AI model"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1563144,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "feels like the thing that\nfeels right in the moment."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1565438,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so yeah, I think in some ways"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1567148,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I actually think it is good"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1568483,
    "dDurationMs": 2086,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that models know and don't behave"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1570569,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "just like a professional therapist would"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1572404,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because that would give the implication"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1574114,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that that's the\nrelationship that they have."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1576116,
    "dDurationMs": 1126,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But yeah, so I don't know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1577242,
    "dDurationMs": 3378,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think it's an interesting future."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1580620,
    "dDurationMs": 1377,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- A few questions about the system prompt,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1581997,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is, you know, in\nour case in Claude.ai,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1583707,
    "dDurationMs": 2168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we give the model a set of instructions"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1585875,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that give it sort of an overall context"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1587460,
    "dDurationMs": 960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for how it should behave."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1588420,
    "dDurationMs": 3628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Tommy asks, \"Why is there\ncontinental philosophy"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1592048,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the system prompt?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1593925,
    "dDurationMs": 1960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And just explain to us what that is."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1595885,
    "dDurationMs": 1919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, so continental philosophy is just,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1597804,
    "dDurationMs": 2920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I mean, literally philosophy\nfrom the European continent."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1600724,
    "dDurationMs": 1626,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so I guess it's seen as kind of like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1602350,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's often more kind of, like, scholarly."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1604352,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It has a lot more"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1606354,
    "dDurationMs": 1961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "kind of like historical\nreferences within it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1608315,
    "dDurationMs": 1876,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "than, say, like analytic philosophy does."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1610191,
    "dDurationMs": 835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Like Foucault or something like that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1611026,
    "dDurationMs": 1084,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, exactly."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1612110,
    "dDurationMs": 1126,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So this was honestly,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1613236,
    "dDurationMs": 3504,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so I think that it has other things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1616740,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in addition to continental philosophy,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1618033,
    "dDurationMs": 2043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but, basically, I think there's\na part of the system prompt,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1620076,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I hope I'm not misremembering,."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1621828,
    "dDurationMs": 2544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that was trying to get Claude\nto be a little bit more,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1624372,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, Claude would just like love to,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1626416,
    "dDurationMs": 1793,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "if you gave Claude a theory,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1628209,
    "dDurationMs": 1669,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it would just love to run with a theory"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1629878,
    "dDurationMs": 1626,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and not really stop and think,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1631504,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, \"Oh, are you making\nlike a scientific claim"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1633798,
    "dDurationMs": 1043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about the world?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1634841,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So if you're like, \"I have this theory,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1636176,
    "dDurationMs": 4504,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is that water is\nactually pure energy"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1640680,
    "dDurationMs": 2628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and, like, that we are getting\nthe life force from water"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1643308,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "when we drink it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1644142,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and that fountains are the thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1645769,
    "dDurationMs": 1167,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we should be putting everywhere,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1646936,
    "dDurationMs": 1127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "just like a, you know?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1648063,
    "dDurationMs": 2544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And you kind of want Claude\nto just have this perspective,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1650607,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is like, \"Is it the case"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1652025,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that this person's making\na kind of scientific claim"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1653735,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about the world"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1654569,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where I should maybe\nbring in relevant facts?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1656696,
    "dDurationMs": 918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Or are they giving me"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1657614,
    "dDurationMs": 2502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a kind of broad like\nworldview or perspective"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1660116,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which isn't necessarily\nmaking empirical claims?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1662160,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so there's all of these view,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1663453,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, so is it just like"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1664913,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a kind of like metaphysical view?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1666331,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Or is it like..."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1667165,
    "dDurationMs": 2377,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so the main reason that it's mentioned"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1669542,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is that when testing this out,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1671586,
    "dDurationMs": 3462,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there was lots of things\nthat if it went too strongly"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1675048,
    "dDurationMs": 917,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the direction of being like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1675965,
    "dDurationMs": 2795,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"Well, every claim is an\nempirical claim about the world,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1678760,
    "dDurationMs": 2586,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it would be very dismissive of just things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1681346,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that are more like exploratory thinking."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1683098,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Unpleasant to talk to."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1683932,
    "dDurationMs": 1626,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, and so it's mostly just like, hey,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1685558,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, it's just illustrative\nexamples of areas"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1688228,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where it's like, \"This might not be making"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1689646,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "empirical claims about the world."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1690939,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This might be much more like a lens"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1692440,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "through which to think about it,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1693274,
    "dDurationMs": 2128,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and just try to make\nthat distinction clear"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1695402,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "when you're thinking through this, Claude."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1697070,
    "dDurationMs": 1126,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Also on the system prompt,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1698196,
    "dDurationMs": 1960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Simon Willison asks, \"So at some point,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1700156,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it said if Claude is asked to count words"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1702283,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or letters or characters,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1703993,
    "dDurationMs": 2628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "then it shouldn't do that.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1706621,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Is that right?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1707455,
    "dDurationMs": 1085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Is that what it said?\n- Basically, yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1708540,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- And apparently that was\nremoved from the system prompt"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1710792,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and Simon wonders why."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1712293,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, so I think it was like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1713878,
    "dDurationMs": 1794,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there used to be a kind\nof like instruction"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1715672,
    "dDurationMs": 1960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for how Claude should do\nthis in the system prompt."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1717632,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Honestly, this is just one of those things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1719342,
    "dDurationMs": 2669,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where I think the models\nprobably just got better."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1722011,
    "dDurationMs": 960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It wasn't necessary,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1722971,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then at that point, you\ncan just like remove it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1724806,
    "dDurationMs": 1043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And there's other things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1725849,
    "dDurationMs": 2085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where you might always want\nit to be in the system prompt"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1727934,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "instead of in the model itself."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1729269,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But in some cases you can\nkind of just train the models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1730937,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to get better or change their behavior."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1733189,
    "dDurationMs": 2878,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Nosson Weissman asks, \"What does it take"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1736067,
    "dDurationMs": 2711,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to be an LLM whisperer at Anthropic?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1738778,
    "dDurationMs": 2378,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Which presumably is a way\nof describing your job."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1741156,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I partly do LLM whispering."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1742824,
    "dDurationMs": 3170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "If you think, I actually,\nlike, want more people"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1745994,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to help with some of the prompting tasks."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1748288,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- If you're an LLM whisperer, contact us."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1750290,
    "dDurationMs": 1209,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- It's a dangerous thing to ask."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1751499,
    "dDurationMs": 2336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Well, okay, okay, yeah, yeah, but."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1753835,
    "dDurationMs": 1209,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- But I think like, it is really hard"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1755044,
    "dDurationMs": 1252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to distill what is going on"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1756296,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "'cause one thing is\njust like a willingness"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1757714,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to interact with the models a lot"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1759382,
    "dDurationMs": 2628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and to like really look\nat output after output"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1762010,
    "dDurationMs": 1918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and to use this to get a sense"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1763928,
    "dDurationMs": 1168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of like the shape of the models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1765096,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and how they respond to different things,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1766806,
    "dDurationMs": 1669,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to be willing to experiment."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1768475,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's actually just like\na very empirical domain."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1770310,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And maybe that's like the thing\nthat people don't often get,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1772562,
    "dDurationMs": 1919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is that prompting is very experimental."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1774481,
    "dDurationMs": 3253,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You deal with, you\nknow, I find a new model"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1777734,
    "dDurationMs": 1543,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I'll be like, I have\na whole different approach"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1779277,
    "dDurationMs": 876,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to how I prompt from that model"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1780153,
    "dDurationMs": 2919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that I find by interacting with it a lot."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1783072,
    "dDurationMs": 1252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think a little\nbit also understanding"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1784324,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how models, like, work."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1786201,
    "dDurationMs": 2085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Sometimes it's also just\nhonestly like reasoning"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1788286,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with the models, which\nis really interesting,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1789621,
    "dDurationMs": 1793,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and really fully explaining the task."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1791414,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This is where I do think\nphilosophy can actually be useful"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1793708,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for prompting in a way"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1795335,
    "dDurationMs": 2878,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because a lot of my\njob is just being like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1798213,
    "dDurationMs": 3837,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I try and explain like\nsome issue or concern"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1802050,
    "dDurationMs": 1960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or thought that I'm having to the model"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1804010,
    "dDurationMs": 1376,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as clearly as possible."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1805386,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then if it does\nsomething kind of unexpected,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1808056,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, you can either ask it why"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1810183,
    "dDurationMs": 876,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or you can try and figure out"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1811059,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what in the thing that you said"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1812811,
    "dDurationMs": 1960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "caused it to kind of misunderstand you,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1814771,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and just like a willingness"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1815605,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to iteratively go through that process."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1817482,
    "dDurationMs": 3295,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Relatedly, Michael Soareverix asks,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1820777,
    "dDurationMs": 3837,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"What do you think of other\nAI whisperers like Janus,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1824614,
    "dDurationMs": 1126,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who is someone online"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1825740,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who is like almost having,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1827200,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, experimental interactions with,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1830662,
    "dDurationMs": 1209,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the way that you've described."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1831871,
    "dDurationMs": 1669,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I think it's really interesting."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1833540,
    "dDurationMs": 4838,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So I love to follow and\nsee the work of people"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1838378,
    "dDurationMs": 2502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who are doing these really\nfascinating experiments"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1840880,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with the model."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1841714,
    "dDurationMs": 2211,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I also think sometimes\ndoing these deep dives"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1843925,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "into the model"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1846344,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and how it thinks of itself,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1847762,
    "dDurationMs": 3670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how it just interacts in\nthese really unusual cases."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1851432,
    "dDurationMs": 2211,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I don't know, I find the\nwork extremely interesting."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1853643,
    "dDurationMs": 1960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think it highlights\nreally interesting depths"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1855603,
    "dDurationMs": 876,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to the models,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1856479,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and in some ways, like, I\nalso think that that community"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1859315,
    "dDurationMs": 2795,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "has been one that kind of can\nhold our feet to the fire,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1862110,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, if they find\nthings that aren't great"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1863987,
    "dDurationMs": 3879,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the system prompt or\nin aspects of the model"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1867866,
    "dDurationMs": 1626,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and its psychology."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1869492,
    "dDurationMs": 2336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- In the sense of, from a\nmodel welfare perspective"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1871828,
    "dDurationMs": 2377,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or from a human welfare\nperspective or both?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1874205,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I mean, I think the two\nare related, so often both."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1876457,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But I do also really appreciate it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1877917,
    "dDurationMs": 2419,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "when it's coming at it from\nthe model welfare perspective."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1880336,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And that includes for future models."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1882171,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So not just things like system prompts,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1883506,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but if you go into the depths of the model"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1885216,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you find some like\ndeep-seated insecurity,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1887218,
    "dDurationMs": 1543,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "then that's really valuable."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1888761,
    "dDurationMs": 835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But that's something"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1889596,
    "dDurationMs": 1459,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that you might actually need\nto kind of try and adjust"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1891055,
    "dDurationMs": 1836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "over the course of time with training"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1892891,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and with giving models more\ninformation and context"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1895351,
    "dDurationMs": 1252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "during training, for example."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1896603,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so, I don't know,\nI appreciate both the,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1898855,
    "dDurationMs": 1376,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, I loved seeing people do"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1900231,
    "dDurationMs": 1085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "these like really interesting,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1901316,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "useful experiments with models,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1902609,
    "dDurationMs": 1584,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but also pointing out ways"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1904193,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in which we can improve things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1906237,
    "dDurationMs": 1919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "through better system prompting"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1908156,
    "dDurationMs": 959,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but also better training"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1909115,
    "dDurationMs": 2211,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and, yeah, I think that's\nreally useful work."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1911326,
    "dDurationMs": 3461,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Couple of questions about safety"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1914787,
    "dDurationMs": 3462,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and maybe the larger risks\nthat these models pose."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1918249,
    "dDurationMs": 2920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Geoffrey Miller asks,\n\"If it became apparent"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1921169,
    "dDurationMs": 2961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that AI alignment was impossible to solve,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1924130,
    "dDurationMs": 1251,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "would you trust that Anthrophic"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1925381,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "would stop trying to develop,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1926966,
    "dDurationMs": 3420,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in his phrase, \"artificial\nsuperintelligence,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1930386,
    "dDurationMs": 1377,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "however you wanna call it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1931763,
    "dDurationMs": 2669,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"and would you have the\nguts to blow the whistle?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1934432,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1935266,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So I guess this feels like"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1936100,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a kind of easy version of the question"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1937977,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because it's like, if it became evident"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1939687,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that it was impossible to align AI models,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1941856,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's not really in anyone's interest"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1943524,
    "dDurationMs": 2586,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to continue to build more powerful models."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1946110,
    "dDurationMs": 2253,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I always hope that I'm\nnot just being pollyannish"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1948363,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about the organization,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1950073,
    "dDurationMs": 2377,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but I do feel like Anthropic\ndoes genuinely care"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1952450,
    "dDurationMs": 2628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about making sure that this goes well"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1955078,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and that it is done in\na way that is very safe"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1957205,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and not deploying models\nthat are, like, dangerous."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1959332,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, a different, like\nslightly harder question"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1961501,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is, like, well, what\nabout being in a world"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1963211,
    "dDurationMs": 2544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where just like there's\nkind of mounting evidence,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1965755,
    "dDurationMs": 2085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's really ambiguous and unclear."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1967840,
    "dDurationMs": 2128,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Right, it's not evident in\nthe way that he describes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1969968,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, yeah, it's not\njust like impossible"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1972095,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but something like it's\ndifficult or we're unsure."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1974931,
    "dDurationMs": 1626,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And in that case, I do like to think"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1976557,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we would be responsible\nenough to be like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1978267,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "look, as models get more capable,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1980269,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's kind of like the standard"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1981896,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that you have to hold yourself to"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1983314,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for showing that those\nmodels are behaving well"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1985441,
    "dDurationMs": 1168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and that you actually have managed"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1986609,
    "dDurationMs": 3837,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to, like, make the models\nhave good values, for example,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1990446,
    "dDurationMs": 3754,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or behave well in the\nworld is going to increase"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1994200,
    "dDurationMs": 2461,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and to behave responsibly\nand in line with that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1996661,
    "dDurationMs": 2669,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think that that is a thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1999330,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that I think the\norganization is going to do"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2001207,
    "dDurationMs": 2044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and a lot of people\ninternally, myself included,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2003251,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "will just hold them to that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2004752,
    "dDurationMs": 3170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "At least I see that as\nlike part of my job,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2007922,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I think many people do."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2009340,
    "dDurationMs": 2461,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Louis says, \"I don't have a question,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2011801,
    "dDurationMs": 1001,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but thanks for offering.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2012802,
    "dDurationMs": 959,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So that's nice.\n- Oh, thank you."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2013761,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- That's nice of him to say, yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2015471,
    "dDurationMs": 2711,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And the final one is\nfrom Real Stale Coffee."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2018182,
    "dDurationMs": 3254,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"What is the last book of fiction you read"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2021436,
    "dDurationMs": 1042,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and did you like it?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2022478,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- The last book that I read was by,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2025314,
    "dDurationMs": 1711,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I hope I'm getting the\npronunciation right,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2027025,
    "dDurationMs": 1793,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Benjamin Labatut,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2028818,
    "dDurationMs": 2377,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it was \"When We Cease\nto Understand the World.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2031195,
    "dDurationMs": 835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Ah, yes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2032030,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- And it's a really interesting book"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2032864,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that becomes kind of increasingly\nfictional as it goes on."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2036784,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think for people working in AI,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2039454,
    "dDurationMs": 2168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's actually a very\ninteresting book to read"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2041622,
    "dDurationMs": 2920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because it's hard to capture\nthe sense of how strange it is"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2044542,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to just exist in the current period"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2046127,
    "dDurationMs": 4004,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where there's just like, I\ndon't know how to describe it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2050131,
    "dDurationMs": 2544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but it's like new things are\nhappening all of the time"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2052675,
    "dDurationMs": 2753,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you don't really have,\nlike, prior paradigms"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2055428,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that can guide you always."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2057263,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so its an interesting book that,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2059265,
    "dDurationMs": 1502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, because it's\nmore about like physics"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2060767,
    "dDurationMs": 917,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and quantum mechanics"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2061684,
    "dDurationMs": 1335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and less actually about the physics"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2063019,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and more about basically this notion"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2064729,
    "dDurationMs": 1376,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of people's reaction to it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2066105,
    "dDurationMs": 2461,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think it's a really interesting book"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2068566,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for people in AI"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2069400,
    "dDurationMs": 1126,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to just capture something"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2070526,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about the kind of like the present moment"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2072528,
    "dDurationMs": 1126,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and how strange it can seem."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2073654,
    "dDurationMs": 1544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But then also, in some ways,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2075198,
    "dDurationMs": 2627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's interesting to like\nlook back on that period"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2077825,
    "dDurationMs": 2628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and how it must have felt to\nmany of the people involved."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2080453,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And now actually it's\na more settled science"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2082705,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and, in some ways, maybe the\nhopeful thing that I have"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2084874,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is that at some point in the\nfuture people will look back"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2086626,
    "dDurationMs": 2377,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and be like, \"Well, you guys\nwere kind of in the dark"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2089003,
    "dDurationMs": 1794,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and trying to like\nreally figure things out,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2090797,
    "dDurationMs": 2168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but now we've settled it all\nand things have gone well.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2092965,
    "dDurationMs": 835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- That'd be nice."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2093800,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- That would be nice."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2094634,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That's the dream."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2095468,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I found an increasing,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2096302,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I read that as well"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2097136,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I found an increasing\nsense of like confusion"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2099972,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as I read through it as it becomes,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2102266,
    "dDurationMs": 3379,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it starts off being quite\nclose to the reality"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2105645,
    "dDurationMs": 3211,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then just sort of becomes\nuntethered as you go on."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2108856,
    "dDurationMs": 1794,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think there's sort\nof a meta issue there"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2110650,
    "dDurationMs": 2043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of, again, like reality becoming stranger"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2112693,
    "dDurationMs": 1043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and stranger and stranger,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2113736,
    "dDurationMs": 2586,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is definitely happening\nto us in the world of AI."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2116322,
    "dDurationMs": 1251,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, though, in the real world,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2117573,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think that reality became stranger"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2119700,
    "dDurationMs": 835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and stranger and stranger"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2120535,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then almost became\nmore understood again."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2122995,
    "dDurationMs": 1085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so, yeah, the hope"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2124080,
    "dDurationMs": 1793,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "would be like maybe that\nwould be true of AI."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2125873,
    "dDurationMs": 1543,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, I do think if we can find ways"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2127416,
    "dDurationMs": 1961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of making this go well,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2129377,
    "dDurationMs": 1918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "then maybe in the future,\nwe'll just look back on this"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2131295,
    "dDurationMs": 918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and be like, \"That was a period"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2132213,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where things were getting\nstranger and stranger,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2133923,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then eventually we\nactually managed to kind of,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2136759,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we did okay"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2137593,
    "dDurationMs": 1794,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and we formed a good understanding\nof it,\" that's the hope."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2139387,
    "dDurationMs": 3879,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "When you're in the middle of\nthe things getting stranger-"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2143266,
    "dDurationMs": 959,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- We're at the weird part right now."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2144225,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yes, you can hope that\nit becomes less weird"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2146060,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "at some point,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2146894,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but I don't know if it's\na fool's hope, but yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2149063,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Well, and I think that's\na nice place to end."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2151065,
    "dDurationMs": 1085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So thank you very much"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2152150,
    "dDurationMs": 2335,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for answering all those\npeople's questions."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2154485,
    "dDurationMs": 2586,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Thank you for Askell-ing\nme the questions."
    } ]
  } ]
}
